quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  22,6,Ekyo nno lwakuba nti mazima Katonda yye ye w'amazima era mazima yye agenda kulamusa abafu. Era nti mazima yye muyinza ku buli kintu
  22,7,"Era nti mazima essaawa ey'enkomerero ejja, teriimu kubuusabuusa era nti mazima ddala Katonda agenda kuzuukiza abali mu kabbuli"
  22,8,Mu bantu mulimu oyo awakanya ebikwata ku Katonda nga tasinziira ku kumanya wadde okulungamizibwa oba ekitabo ekiraga obutangaavu
  22,9,"(Mu ngeri y’okulengezza n’okwekuza) aweta ensingoye abe nga ajja abantu ku kkubo lya Katonda, atuusibwako okuswazibwa mu nsi era tugenda kumukombesa ku lunaku lw'enkomerero ku bibonerezo ebyokya"
  22,10,(Aligambibwa nti) ekyo kikutUuseeko olw'ebyo e mikonogyo bye gyakola edda (ku nsi) era mazima Katonda talyazAamaanya baddu
  22,11,Ne mu bantu mulimu asinza Katonda ng'ali ku ndeboolebo (ya bukkiriza) n'olwekyo bwatuukibwako ekirungi akkalira nakyo ate bwatuukibwako ekikemo oba okugesezebwa atalantuka n'agwira ku kyenyikye (naava ku ddiini) olwo nno naafiirwa ensi n'enkomerero okwo kwe kufaafaaganirwa okw'olwatu
  22,12,Alekawo Katonda n'aasinza ebyo ebitamutuusaako kabi era ebitamutuusaako mugaso okwo kwe kubula okwewala
  22,13,"Asaba oyo akabiike nga ke kali okumpi okusinga omugasogwe, mubi nnyo asuubirwa okutaasa era mubi nnyo asuubirwa okuba nga ye w'omukwano"
  22,14,"Mazima Katonda agenda kuyingiza e jjana abo abaakola emirimu emirungi, nga emigga gikulukutira wansi, waazo, mazima Katonda akola ekyo kyaba ayagadde"
  22,15,Omuntu alowooza nti Katonda tagenda kutaasa Mubakawe kuno ku nsi ne ku nkomerero kimugwanidde akasuke omuguwa waggulu ku kasolya oluvanyuma yeerippe (yeetuge) olwo nno alabe abaffe byakola bisobola okumuwonya byatayagala